reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This sweater was for my son and he loves it! The fit was appropriate to size and the material is soft and well made. The colors are true to what is in the picture too. I would certainly buy this again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice men’s sweater
reviews.reviewText: Product seems to be well made and a tad long in sleeves and torso. Still need to wash it for the first time to see if any shrinkage occurs. My husband likes it and it looks nice on him.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super Comfortable and Very Stylish
reviews.reviewText: This was shockingly one of the most comfortable sweaters I have ever purchased. It fits me very well. The color is not as displayed (slightly more burnt orange), but that is a plus to me. It washed perfectly fine. I allowed it to air dry and it didn't wrinkle or bulge anywhere. Highly highly recommended. Will be buying the other colors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Thick and nice hues
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for family photos. My husband is picky about his shirts but he does well with color block sweaters. I was pleasantly surprised on how thick and heavy this sweater was. Colors are very good and would be great for any shade of other colors to match. No complaints it’s been repeatedly worn for various holiday parties. Husband is 6’2” and 207 he also has a long torso and it was long in sleeve and shirt length which is hard to find for my husband.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Got this for my very tall son for Christmas. He is 6’5” and the xxl was flattering and a good length. The knit is medium weight and the colors are nice. The yarn is soft, not scratchy. A good value!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice sweater
reviews.reviewText: Hubby loved it! He wore it for his birthday dinner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love this sweater. It’s light weight and looks and feels great. It’s a good purchase
